						<div class="postbody">Before we start sorry my bad english and i hope you understand it anyway <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" /><br /><br />So my Story begins 10 Years ago. I was 13 years old and was playing in my Room. Excactly at 9pm 2 of my Family Pictures was falling of the walls for no good Reason. Confiused about that i went done to my Parents to tell them what happend. After i opened the door to the livingroom i saw that all of our Family Pictures was lay on the floor except for 3. I looked at my Mother and asked her what happen. She answered that she diddnt know so i told her that this thing happend in my Room too. <br />After we finished hanging the Pictures up again i went to bed... In the morning i heard my mother crying and screaming my name. I ran to her she told me that my Grandfather died. We drove to the doctors office to ask why and on what time he died. The doc told us that my grandfather died the day befor on 9:30pm so 30minutes later after the pictures was falling down. We went home after that we looked at all Pictures who was falling down. And on every Family Picture was my grandfather with us on it. Only the 2 who dont fall he dont was on it. But this was not the only thing after my grandfathers furneral i was laying on my bed trying to fell asleep. After one hour of trying it was starting to get cold in my room. And i heared a whisper its said &quot;dont be sad about my death, you have to be strong for me and for your family&quot; . Soon after its start to getting warm again cuz it was in the middle of the summer. After that i finally fell asleep. I dont know if this was a dream or not. But on the next day on my way home from school i stoped at the cementery my grandfather was buried. I visited his Grave layed down some flowers and whisperd &quot;i will be strong&quot;. <br /><br />Then i start go back out of the cementary because everytime i passed the cementary gates i start having this feeling of beeing watched. Maybe its because in the daytime many people are there to maintain the graves of  family members or friends. But this feeling is not like if a normal living people are looking at me no its more of anything is watching me. hm<br /><br />Anyway thats the story why i start to like so creepy and scary stuff. <br />Again sorry for the bad english iam trying my best <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><br />~dere<br />Chris</div>

